column5: We've got two new team members added just in time for the bass opener.. Live2Fish is on Team 1 Zib is on Team 8  For those still wanting to get on a team, sign up by replying to the Sign Up thread in the main tourney forum!
thanks Rick.  Hope to contribute some big fish team 1
Thanks Rick... although that doesn't say team 5 lol... welcome guys to your teams...
Not everybody can be on the winning team Jen!  I wish the newcomers the best of luck!
